      "title": "Theory: White Plays 6 Bg5, Delaying Nf3",
      "description": "Introduction to the 6 Bg5 line in the early h2-h3 system. Black prepares ...e7-e5 with ...Na6 and ...Qe8.",
      "textContext": "Pages 151-153 of Starting Out: The King's Indian",
      "preparsedJson": {
        "game_id": "h3_bg5_theory",
